title: Facebook To Launch New Platform For Entrepreneurial Journalists: Report
text: Facebook Inc (NASDAQ: FB) is exploring a new publishing platform to allow journalists to create their own websites and newsletters. What Happened: The yet-to-be-named new platform will be integrated with Facebook's pages platform, Axios reports.

title: Facebook (FB) Strikes Deal With News Corp (NWSA) in Australia
text: Facebook (FB) strikes multi-year pay deal with NWSA and boosts content through paid partnerships with Australian news outlets amid rising concerns over dominance of online advertising.

title: News Corporation (NWSA) Inks Deal With Facebook in Australia
text: News Corporation (NWSA) reaches a three-year agreement with Facebook in Australia for providing news in exchange of payments.

title: Rupert Murdoch's News Corp Inks Deal To Resolve Facebook's Australian Content Blackout: Report
text: News Corp (NASDAQ: NWSA) became the first media outlet to reach a content-supply deal in Australia with Facebook Inc (NASDAQ: FB). It attempted to resolve the latter's brief blackout in protest against the country's new content law, which sought an arbitrator as a last resort to finalize the payment terms, Reuters reports.

title: Facebook has struck a deal to pay Rupert Murdoch's News Corp for news content in Australia
text: Facebook has signed a content-supply deal with Rupert Murdoch's News Corp in Australia, the companies said on Tuesday, weeks after the social media giant briefly cut off access to news in the country. The agreement makes News Corp the first major media outlet to strike a Facebook deal under controversial new laws that let an Australian government-appointed arbitrator set fees if companies fail to do so. Terms of the deal were not disclosed.

title: Facebook signs deal with Murdoch's News Corp in Australia
text: Facebook is teaming up with News Corp Australia just weeks after the country passed a groundbreaking law requiring tech companies to pay for news content.

title: Facebook and News Corp Strike Pay Deal for Australian Content
text: The deal follows a standoff over legislation passed by the Australian government to compensate publishers.
